headline: RPM International (RPM) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: RPM International (RPM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +7.50% and +3.21%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
